717674f-b.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 81st Street (West)
717674f-b.text:
Broadway, north from W. 81st Street as photographed from
a point to the south of same. To the right, at the S.E. corner
of 81st Street is Eeiths' 81st Street Theatre. Note on the same
side the new apartment house under construction at the N.E.
corner of 82nd Street. The Forres (No. 2261-71) and the Saxony
(No. 227E-79) are at the left, occupying the weat aide frontage
of Broadway from 81st to 8Cnd Streets. These photos apoeared
in the publication 'Silver Jubilee of Greater New York.
